Description: Should be nicknamed 'Tornado Turnover'. How is this man paid nearly $20 million a year?
Promising rookie. Strong ability to drive to basket. Must work on jump shot.
Beast in the paint. Almost broke NBA FG% record. If Knicks trade him, I am done.
Has athletic potential. Instead, looks like a baby giraffe on the court.
First 2 years were garbage. Finally starting to show up in the 2019-20 season. Let's go Frankie!
